         <div type="traslation">
            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>The Devīmāhātmya, which was begun in the Kollam [year] 1083, month of Āṣāḍha, 10th
               day, was completed on the 21st day. Honour to śrī Mahādevī. Śrī. Prosperity.
               Nārāyaṇan son of Sundaran copied (°lakhitaṃ, emend into °likhitaṃ) [it] with his own
               hand.</p>
         </div>
